<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَسْلَمَ}</span> ... انْقَادَ، وَاسْتَسْلَمَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَنِيفًا}</span> ... مَائِلًا عَنِ الشَّرْكِ إِلَى التَّوْحِيدِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
