<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأُحْضِرَتِ الأَنفُسُ الشُّحَّ}</span> ... جُبِلَتْ عَلَى الشُّحِّ وَالْبُخْلِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَذَرُوهَا}</span> ... تَتْرُكُوهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَالْمُعَلَّقَةِ}</span> ... الَّتِي لَيْسَتْ بِذَاتِ زَوْجٍ، وَلَا مُطَلَّقَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
